content: This app is phenomenal for what it does but it is missing one thing that would make this app a true 5 star rating worthy which would be quest search. Even without that this is a great app.
replyContent: Thats a great idea! I'll look into adding it. Thank you for the review :)

content: Ive tried other apps to look up quests, beasts, players, skills and GE and everything. But never had i seen an app that did ALL that in one. This is a well made, designed snd intuitive app. I opened it and felt it was easy to navigate, understand. I loved everything it had. Literally made me delete a few others i had cause this gave me the info better. I even plan to spread the word so others can use it as well and know of it. Curious if its on ios though.
Its exactly the same as the free version. There is literally no reason to spend the dollar in this app.
Simple, clean, and snappy app. Perfect for any RS player who needs some quick stats and references. Really well put together!
